    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeon Adventure Gang is a co-op top-down multiplayer roguelike where you and three other adventurers team up to explore this unmarked dungeon as far as possible. Explore, gear up, reunite, and push on. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147690/extras/3f020938d8dc765a8b2335529b95b450.avif?t=1730153318\" width=614 height=204 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Randomly generated dungeons, each with random rooms, random pathing, random loot, and more! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple classes each with varying gameplay styles &amp; mechanics! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple dungeon styles with varying enemy pools! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam integrated online multiplayer along with support for locally hosted servers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Controller Support! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with friends and discover everything the dungeon has to offer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>                                                                                                                                                        </u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147690/extras/24f617fb7850732134ab39034f523ba0.apng?t=1730153318\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147690/extras/24f617fb7850732134ab39034f523ba0.poster.avif?t=1730153318\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=140 /></picture></span></p>",
